<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
input
|> Kino.Input.read()
|> String.split("\n", trim: true)
|> Enum.map(&String.to_integer/1)
|> Enum.chunk_every(2, 1, :discard)
|> Enum.filter(fn [left, right] -> right > left end)
|> Enum.count()
```
